SUMMARY:SwatPDX Book Club
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['College Advancement']\\nCategory: Meeting\\nWe
 ’re on our 4th SwatPDX book club meeting and would love to have you join
  us on Tuesday\, May 12\, 7-9 p.m. The book selection is Train Dreams by
  Denis Johnson. The meeting address is an alum’s Portland home in Raleig
 h Hills and will be sent to attendees a few days before the meeting. Plea
 se RSVP for the book club by May 5. The form includes a section to indic
 ate your interest in future book club meetings and to receive communicatio
 ns about other SwatPDX events\, even if you can’t attend the May book cl
 ub meeting. We hope to see you at one of our events! Sincerely\, Ana Cragn
 olino ’93\, Catherine Rose ’97\, and Becky Voorheis ’93SwatPDX co-le
 ads  \\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3De
 vent%26eventid%3D1391946007
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1391946007
CATEGORIES:Meeting
END:VEVENT
