SUMMARY:Philadelphia Connection Woodmere Art Museum Tour
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['College Advancement']\\nCategory: Exhibit\\nWoo
 dmere Art Museum Tour Charles Knox Smith Hall9201 Germantown AvenuePhilade
 lphia $15 per personRSVP TodayThis landmark exhibition celebrates the fift
 y-year career of former Swarthmore professor Syd Carpenter. Together\, we 
 will explore her evocative ceramic sculptures that weave together African 
 American history\, ancestral lands\, and the beauty of the natural world. 
 It is a wonderful opportunity to engage with profound art while reconnecti
 ng with your local alumni community. Then join us for an optional group lu
 nch after the tour to continue our conversations. Lunch venue details will
  be shared very soon. Warmly\,The Philadelphia Connection Committee\\nDeta
 ils: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventi
 d%3D1393647296
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1393647296
CATEGORIES:Exhibit
END:VEVENT
