DTSTAMP:20260429T121940Z
DTSTART:20260604T153000Z
DTEND:20260604T173000Z
SUMMARY:Garnet Day
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ["President's Office"]\\nCategory: Reception\\nJo
 in our annual tradition of celebrating Swarthmore seniors during May’s G
 arnet Day! Please note that\, since Thursday is the first day of exams\, G
 arnet Day will be on Wednesday this month. Garnet Day Celebration of the C
 lass of 2026 Wednesday\, May 6 4-6 p.m. Pearson Lawn There will be carniva
 l games\, music\, and an array of snacks\, including treats from Weckerly
 ’s\, Lil’ Pop Shop\, and the Dia Dolce cupcake truck. Vegan\, vegetari
 an\, and gluten-free food options will be available. Everyone’s favorite
  feathered friend\, Phineas\, will also make an appearance!  We hope you 
 can stop by to congratulate our seniors on their remarkable accomplishment
 s\, and wish them a wonderful future ahead. As always\, remember to wear y
 our Swarthmore gear to show your spirit!  \\nDetails: https://swatcentral
 .swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1281162995
LOCATION:Old Science Hall Lawn
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1281162995
CATEGORIES:Reception
END:VEVENT
